OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLorry driver shortage:     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGovernment to lift rules on
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fforeign haulier deliveries 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The rules on the number of deliveries  
OL,6, overseas lorry drivers can make in the 
OL,7, UK are set to be relaxed in a bid to   
OL,8, tackle supply chain problems in the    
OL,9, run-up to Christmas.                   
OL,11,FUnder the new plans, drivers will be   
OL,12,Fable to make unlimited deliveries or   
OL,13,Fcollections within a 14 day period.    
OL,15,FCurrently EU drivers can only make two 
OL,16,Fpick-ups or drop-offs each week.       
OL,18,FIt is hoped the changes will happen by 
OL,19,FDecember - but UK drivers fear they    
OL,20,Fmight lose work to cheaper EU rivals.  
